docker search --help
Usage:	docker search [OPTIONS] TERM
Search the Docker Hub for images

Options:
-f, --filter filter   Filter output based on conditions provided 【过滤输出的内容】
--format string   Pretty-print search using a Go template
--limit int       Max number of search results (default 25)
--no-trunc        Don't truncate output 【 不截断输出内容】

docker search 默认情况下返回 25 个结果
--filter
stars
    eg: docker search --filter=stars=100 mysql
is-official => 官方构建
    eg: docker search --filter=is-official=true mysql
is-automated => 自动化构建
    eg: docker search --filter=is-automated=true mysql